last_episode_to_air.name: Miles Kane and The Mysterines
last_episode_to_air.overview: The final episode brings back Miles Kane and his band, and a second appearance from The Mysterines joining Paul’s band, with vocalist Lia Metcalfe sharing vocal duties with Paul on his version of Dr John’s “Walk On Gilded Splinters”.

name: The Black Barn Sessions
overview: This December, Paul unveils an exciting new project! Inviting some of his favourite talents to his studio ‘Black Barn’!
